  "description": "box-and-box \u2014 faithful runtime of the seven-rung modality ladder plus the resource economy beneath it: alethic, axiological, deontic, temporal, reflexive, epistemic, strategic, and resource (linear/reusable accounting with conservation, capacity-as-continual-learning, and Type-II pricing of the ladder's repair operators). One bridge composes them. 97 laws property-tested.",
